From Ken Darcovich Subject west coast NHL playoff games Us easterners who have newspapers with editors unsympathetic to playoff pools often don't get summaries from west coast games since they finish too late at night for the morning I and I'm sure others too would greatly appreciate it if scoring summaries of west coast playoff games could be posted to this group right basically all we need are goal scorers and assists don't bother with times penalties shots this would make a lot of pool obsessed people very I guess with the Senators out golfing now the local papers have lost